INSERT INTO `t_blog` VALUES (33, 1, '超级笔记supernote', '【日经新闻】比iPad更适合书写？上手热门电子纸产品“超级笔记”', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">本报道转载至日经新闻&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">作者：大吉紗央里（おおよしさおり）</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">原文链接：</span><a href=\"https://tech.nikkeibp.co.jp/atcl/nxt/column/18/00160/081600137/?P=1\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">https://tech.nikkeibp.co.jp/atcl/nxt/column/18/00160/081600137/?P=1</a></p><p><br></p><p>在日本，有一个电子纸产品已成为“随性书写”的热门话题。它是由中国上海雷塔智能科技有限公司（Ratta）开发的“超级笔记”。笔者于2019年6月参观ISOT东京文具展时，看到 Superote的官方展台人山人海，游客们在现场就立马购买超级笔记。</p><p><br></p><p>Ratta于2019年8月7日开始在日本亚马逊试销Supernote，有两种型号可供选择：A5尺寸（10.3英寸）“Supernote A5”和A6尺寸（7.8英寸）“Supernote A6”。在日本，目前只有Supernote A5在售，价格为63，800日元（不含税）。</p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/9eb700b5-114b-4f20-b101-f5b22012bf67.jpg?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=R%2Bq4wrbRXuvPpKO83MtIQdgzQB8%3D\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\">Supernote A5，价格为63，800日元（不含税）。包含主机、封套、type-c数据线以及Supernote Pen。</p><p><br></p><p>这次，我们将通过实际使用Supernote A5来介绍它的功能特性。</p><p><br></p><p>Supernote使用特殊的手写笔在电子纸上书写文字和图画。您可以创建包含多个页面的笔记（就像传统纸质笔记）以及添加或删除笔记页面，还可以根据需求切换不同的笔记模板，诸如空白、网格和水平线等。</p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/6e00de2b-1438-4b62-a49c-2897b694822e.jpg?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=wRBjzXDEsDtOFmV0Sq7lElG0Bjg%3D\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">超过10种类型的笔记本模板。就个人而言，画面左边有线的“清单式”模板使用起来很方便。</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">它还具有文档阅读功能，可以阅读EPUB、PDF格式的电子书，资料和图片。最重要的是，您可以在文档中手写笔记或标上可搜索的符号。</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">无论在哪个页面，你都可以自由选择笔型，粗细和颜色。笔的种类有画均匀细线的“针管笔”，可以根据笔的压感改变粗细的“水笔”和绘制粗线的“马克笔”。此外，它还具有选择和移动手写内容，复制和粘贴，撤销和恢复等多种功能。</span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/8419be75-8f77-4216-98a6-5b3c42191397.jpg?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=LG%2FZsybsLAmvN4h0k8fzQ9w%2FuLA%3D\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">滑动屏幕左侧可以选择笔型，粗细和颜色等。在校对资料和描画重点笔记内容时使用浅灰色的笔来做标记会很方便。</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Supernote A5主机的存储容量为32GB。它配备了Wi-Fi通信功能，您可以通过电子邮件发送笔记或将其上传到容量为32 GB的专用云存储。不过，Supernote没有内置Web浏览器。</span></p><p><br></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\">手写延迟低至28毫秒，畅快书写</strong></p><p><br></p><p>Supernote的最大魅力在于书写体验，兼顾了书写的流畅和真实感。</p><p><br></p><p>说到在显示器上用专用笔手写的工具，代表性的是iPad和Apple Pencil的组合。代表手写反应速度“延迟(从移动笔到在画面上显示的时间)”达到了20毫秒，移动笔时几乎能同时画出线，毫无迟滞感。</p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"background-color: white;\">Supernote的手写反应速度也非常快。Ratta在官网中表示“Supernote配备自主研发的独立读写芯片，书写延迟仅为28ms”，可以说在手写延迟上与iPad+Apple Pencil非常接近。在实际的商务活动中尝试把Supernote用于记笔记，从没有在书写时感到过迟滞。</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"background-color: white;\">Supernote书写的感觉与传统文具相似，尤其在“写”的舒适度上体现。与iPad+Apple Pencil的组合相比的话，因为iPad是在玻璃材质的“硬屏幕”上用Apple Pencil的“软笔尖”进行书写，所以造成了iPad+Apple Pencil的书写感觉与传统文具完全不一样。</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"background-color: white;\">与此相对，Supernote与真实纸笔的书写感觉相当接近，因为它是用硬笔尖写在软质手写膜上，接近于用极细的油性记号笔书写的感觉，写起来比iPad舒服，而且特别容易写细小的文字。我在平时的工作洽谈中有很多时候需要写“文字、插图和图解”，我觉得Supernote非常适合这样的用途。</span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/fb455476-775a-4a63-8b11-34884a092f49.jpg?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=KpXEezGhGs8GQKmYGcOxzPNzEj4%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">iPad Pro（左）和Supernote（右）的比较。在Supernote中更容易手写精细字符。</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Supernote A5的屏幕虽然是台湾E Ink Holdings的电子纸“Carta”，但它最大的特点是其表面的手写软膜。这种特制软膜具备高强度，除非用尖锐物体故意划伤，否则不会出现破损。</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">配套笔是Ratta采用Wacom技术开发的专用手写笔Supernote Pen。笔尖为0.7mm，硬度达到了3H。</span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/bbade915-8078-4ca3-adb2-0b21919639ad.jpg?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=Pmaqrvtwyt4qfiNZ%2FcchUxT5bZU%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Apple Pencil（上）和Supernote Pen（下）有着完全不同的笔尖。</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p>硬笔+软膜的组合带来了非常愉悦的书写体验，尤其是你在书写时能感觉到有一个阻力将笔尖推入指尖，你甚至可以在不凝视屏幕的情况下进行书写。</p><p><br></p><p>这层干性的软膜不会让你留下指纹痕迹，除此之外，即使您的手侧面无意间触碰屏幕，也不会导致误触，因此您完全可以把优势手的侧面靠在屏幕上进行书写。</p><p><br></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\">笔无需充电，而设备一次充电可以使用一周</strong></p><p><br></p><p>请记住，电子纸有一个特殊的缺陷。首先，因为它使用单色屏幕，与iPad不同，它不适合彩色绘画。其次，当你翻页时，有时会看到上一个页面的残影，这是电子纸特有的现象，在页面刷新后残影就会消失。</p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/3c991d84-b8ae-4ddb-88b3-5c01419fdc96.jpg?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=UhI2d%2FULB328b5AM9REKjmOwLVg%3D\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">有时会看到上一个页面的残影，这是电子纸特有的现象。通过右侧滑条手动向上滑，可以刷新屏幕并清理残影。</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/bbcf211e-275c-4d25-a045-52f2287f0cb2.jpg?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=qWxcv9LiHJ%2FLUthOllyq2qQckPQ%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">这是清除残影后的状态，如果从上到下滑动右侧滑动条则可以查看标签菜单</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Ratta将Supernote称为“数字文具”。您可以在Supernote上看到很多还原传统文具的特质，比如真实的书写体验。</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">这一点同样表现在外观上。Supernote附带的标准笔采用了笔帽的设计，看起来就像传统圆珠笔。他们正积极与世界各地的文具制造商合作，例如以圆珠笔闻名的法国BIC，您似乎可以期待一场能够激发文具爱好者心灵的合作。</span></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/49ee0b00-16ee-4c48-9e28-b159382bf7f0.jpg?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=MJVToCi0R7Fn6aryEPQiNUcxX1g%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">A5和A6尺寸有各种样式和材质的封套，Supernote专用笔有多种设计，预计未来会越来越多。</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p>虽然有着传统文具般的触感和温暖，但它也是一种数字设备。数字设备往往在携带时充电是一个问题，但电子纸比LCD显示器更节能，电池寿命也更长。Supernote A5的电池容量为2850 mAh，如果每天使用2-3小时，则只需每周充电一次。Supernote使用的是USB Type-C口进行充电。</p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/597eb651-089c-4563-be98-eb8e16a8c4bd.jpg?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=HENoK7wluxMBB8pDljS4xvhi0D0%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">机身顶部有一个电源按钮</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p>在iPad上，笔（Apple Pencil）也需要充电，但Supernote的专用笔不需要充电。这是因为采用了电磁感应技术，只要主机的电池电量没有耗尽，您就可以书写笔记。</p><p><br></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\">兼备数字设备的智能，轻松共享文档</strong></p><p><br></p><p>Supernote还具有许多数字设备独有的功能，特别是对于文档的存储和共享，它具有传统纸笔无法实现的便利功能。</p><p><br></p><p>在很多工作场景中，手写信息需要以数字方式共享和存储。以往这很麻烦，例如，当您想与整个团队共享手写的粗略草稿时，您只能使用智能手机相机拍摄或使用多功能设备扫描并发送附加到电子邮件的图像或PDF文件，而保存它们也要像这样复杂操作。</p><p><br></p><p>如果您用Supernote A5书写笔记草稿，则可以使用Wi-Fi直接发送笔记，或将数据存储在专用云盘中，共享笔记可以选择PDF或PNG格式。</p><p><br></p><p>在参加会议时，使用Supernote进行文档和手稿批注也非常方便。您只需提前导入材料，便可以在会议现场写下批注，并在会议结束时通过电子邮件发送出去。</p><p><br></p><p>如果您将它用作文档阅读器，突然有了灵感和想法。在这种情况下，您可以在屏幕中画一条横线，便会出现分屏笔记界面，您可以在其中记录您的灵感。</p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/403e8d01-5676-4925-8fee-89c761c90767.jpg?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=7TcWDBwxkmKygA39457ht7axI3w%3D\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">您可以在阅读电子书时做分屏笔记</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">虽然Supernote是一种数字设备，但它的作用相比于传统笔记有过之而无不及。在输入工作上，比如同步智能手机与计算机上的内容或查收电子邮件，它更有效率。而在输出工作上，比如笔记和素描，它也还原了传统笔记本的体验。</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">目前在日本的贩售还算是试売阶段。在日本Amazon以外的线上或线下通路也予定贩售，目前在日本的贩售台数还不多，客服窗口并非日本专用，不过全球的邮件客服可提供日语服务。</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">超级笔记Supernote</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">现已入驻海内外线上商城及多家线下体验门店</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">线上商城</strong></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://mall.jd.com/index-837318.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">京东官方旗舰店</a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">有赞官方旗舰店</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/B07VK7ZVZG?ref=myi_title_dp\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">亚马逊日本旗舰店</a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><a href=\"https://goodereader.com/blog/?s=supernote&amp;post_type=product&amp;title=1&amp;excerpt=1&amp;content=1&amp;categories=1&amp;attributes=1&amp;tags=1&amp;sku=1&amp;orderby=date-DESC&amp;ixwps=1\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Good e-Reader Store（全球供货）</a></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">线下体验</strong></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">百新书局</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">上海市浦东新区银城路66号303-307&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">上海市长宁区天山路345号东楼2层&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">上海市黄浦区福州路364号</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">百脑汇乐之</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">上海市徐家汇漕溪北路339号</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">外文书店</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">上海市黄浦区福州路390号</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">杭晓通信</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">浙江省永康市西城街道胜利街222号</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/690a33e0-c67b-4251-bf46-dbe48e4663c9.gif?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=95dQZbVRK0GB9OYlEYijLZHQNdg%3D\"></p>', 'https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/6051f503-922d-44d6-bff3-80829c97af9a.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&Expires=&Signature=tmISrPKpRG62%2B8nBmgo6NVENLlM%3D', 'https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/980b66ce-291b-49ad-aea9-a37739255e6c.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&Expires=&Signature=v9rl%2FZw3fkIffVlIrcs1lwpHDd4%3D', '0', 'ZH-CN', 92, 91, 10, 17, 19, 18, 'Y', '2019-10-16 22:53:22', 'admin', '2019-11-05 16:08:27', 'admin', '【日经新闻】比iPad更适合书写？上手热门电子纸产品“超级笔记”222', '【日经新闻】比iPad更适合书写？上手热门电子纸产品“超级笔记”', '【日经新闻】比iPad更适合书写？上手热门电子纸产品“超级笔记”');
INSERT INTO `t_blog` VALUES (34, 2, '超级笔记supernote', '接受波澜不惊的人生？去做个劈波斩浪的勇者吧', '<p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/22c6b268-905c-4491-bda8-789676ee3cb8.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=Du4WZdl5oFj9EHja5%2BAuHjB3Xag%3D\"></p><p>随着高等教育的普及，越来越多的人在校园毕业后，会选择大公司，一头钻进这艘巨轮，在安稳的舱室中随波逐流，如同巨型机器里的一颗颗螺丝钉，平静地度过波澜不惊的一生。</p><p><br></p><p>他是一个有梦想的人。</p><p><br></p><p>他所在的公司是一个知名大公司，而他却只是其中平凡的一员，每天重复着枯燥的工作内容，应付着冗长的任务流程，处理着复杂的人际关系。</p><p><br></p><p>他最近迷上了励志鸡汤，每天下班后在床上都要先读一篇“成功学”再睡觉。</p><p><br></p><p>这天，公司开设了一个新项目，是他所擅长的，他很兴奋，觉得终于可以施展自己的能力了。他满怀期待地收到了上司安排的任务，和往常一样枯燥重复。他发现这个项目细节上有很多可以创新的地方，鼓起勇气写了一份建议报告交到了上司手里，上司标志性地笑着点了点头，把报告放在桌角，再也没提起过。</p><p><br></p><p>从最后一班公交里下来，他精疲力尽地打开房门瘫在床上，又到了每晚睡觉前的励志鸡汤时间了。</p><p><br></p><p>他瞥了一眼斜躺在床角的“成功学”，突然意识到，自己离成功好像越来越远了。</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong>1</strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(174, 163, 162);\">&gt;</strong><strong style=\"color: rgb(125, 116, 108);\">&gt;</strong><strong>螺丝钉</strong><strong style=\"color: rgb(125, 116, 108);\">&lt;</strong><strong style=\"color: rgb(174, 163, 162);\">&lt;</strong></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">2008年，一部仅有7分钟的阿根廷动画短片轰动了世界，一经上映就包揽了ANIMA-科多巴国际动画电影节评委会大奖、安纳西国际动画节电影节国际影评人费比西奖、利尔达拉美电影节最佳短片奖等102项大奖。</span></p><p><br></p><iframe class=\"ql-video\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?origin=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com&amp;vid=h1359pc0c8j&amp;autoplay=false&amp;full=true&amp;show1080p=false&amp;isDebugIframe=false\" height=\"380.8125\" width=\"677\"></iframe><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">这部短片的名字叫《螺丝人生》，全程没有音乐，没有对白，从第一幕开始就充满了诡异的气氛。</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/d4566143-8a1d-4a83-8283-6fc073dc5a1d.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=i7LL5ZxhiNQFZdSear9Nlq%2FnIAc%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/19b98e74-429c-4a93-8f2e-4a303570b1c1.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=%2F7hTytRMmYMJMSUEc%2FwuD4ycvs8%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">早上七点一刻，闹钟响起，一个秃头男子半眯着眼睛站起身来，极不情愿地关掉了闹钟。秃头男子起床第一件事是去打开台灯，令人奇怪的是，这个台灯是由一个人来支撑的。</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19); background-color: rgb(238, 237, 235);\"><img src=\"data:image/gif;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAADUlEQVQImWNgYGBgAAAABQABh6FO1AAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==\"></span></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/622b9dd4-4bba-4a40-855f-c6d4a88c1921.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=Eojh%2BUIt07jXdx4HqJ%2B9WVqaNyE%3D\"></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/81d009b0-50df-4818-992a-d5d82bfca68f.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=mJCQE3GjrjsAMF4aTPM5qvxv1TI%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">随后，秃头男子洗漱的镜子、吃饭的椅子，甚至是打的“出租车”，也都是活生生的人，这些人仿佛机器一样，毫无表情。</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">看到这里，不禁让人猜想，秃头男子的身份很可能是一位达官贵人。</span></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/d3c2db2e-b285-4276-98a4-8e6d6e4178d7.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=p%2BK9sy0%2BIKZtcinYzf9s2FsYX4I%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/cb24a063-a9a8-470b-8235-00d1ab8f0686.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=Rtt0UstKdk%2B2dVUTpuoXTHSRwZg%3D\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19); background-color: rgb(238, 237, 235);\"><img src=\"data:image/gif;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAADUlEQVQImWNgYGBgAAAABQABh6FO1AAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==\"></span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">一路来到公司，短片接近尾声，秃头男子也乘坐由“胖子”运作的电梯到达了最高层的办公室，他的身份终于要揭开了。</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">西装革履，气派大楼，一路被人服务，他究竟是怎样一个上层人物？</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/2679897c-10e6-4647-ba2b-c9c4f5a1ec4a.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=9%2F7kwydL4AiNlYfTxBV3HAJO%2FuM%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">然而，让所有人都没想到是，秃头男子竟缓缓俯身，趴倒在地，面无表情，任由他人踩过。</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">原来，他每天的工作就是来到这里趴在地上，替人擦鞋。</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">七分钟的短片，让人倒吸一口凉气。</span></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/a87f9bb5-45c0-4e74-bb7a-026ba12509cf.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=uqE3t4N%2FcePgQya2XFsd1wI2WX0%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">片中的每个人都像工具一样，每天出现在重复的位置，机械地重复着相同的工作，面无表情，毫无情绪，就像社会机器里的一颗颗螺丝。</span></p><p><br></p><p>这部短片是想告诉人们在这个社会中工作多么无奈吗？</p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19); background-color: rgb(238, 237, 235);\"><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/520a0bfa-04b1-40eb-b6d9-4dcd4f75421f.gif?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=raSRsxjmjBJ9oaJNDqquI23jPcM%3D\"><img src=\"data:image/gif;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAADUlEQVQImWNgYGBgAAAABQABh6FO1AAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==\"></span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">片尾，黑色画面里出现一个头顶灯罩的人，是之前秃头男子家里那个台灯。</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">他把头顶的灯罩拿下来，仔细凝视了一会后，重重地摔在了地上，扬长而去。</span></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/4ebd4766-b84b-49dc-949a-0588ee93f40c.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=qgUy75Iz6xQcE%2B%2BT45jD%2FeIECDc%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">他不是放弃工作，而是放弃做一颗被定制的螺丝钉。</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">在这个社会工作固然无奈，但是你有选择和创造自己人生的权力。</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong>2</strong></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(242, 238, 223);\">&nbsp;</strong><strong style=\"color: rgb(174, 163, 162);\">&gt;</strong><strong style=\"color: rgb(125, 116, 108);\">&gt;</strong><strong>顶梁柱</strong><strong style=\"color: rgb(125, 116, 108);\">&lt;</strong><strong style=\"color: rgb(174, 163, 162);\">&lt;</strong></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">大公司就像一台已经运行很长时间的机器，存在着既定的做事方式。一旦你走进去，你就会知道你的具体工作是什么，你如何融入你的部门，你会收获一种稳定感。</span></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/9cbe96e4-8532-4af0-a5c9-e8cfda9182bd.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=hYvkCLHsXnWZJjpgHgWBnXOl4Lg%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">但是，对于你雄心勃勃施展本领的计划，在一家大公司里可能会遇到很多阻碍。即使这家公司对新想法很开放，想要做出改变或是增加一些新的内容也会花费大量时间。</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">2010年5月，传奇设计大师Matias Duarte离开Palm，进入谷歌担任Android的新用户体验总监。Duarte早先就制定好了一套Android全面更新计划，然而在谷歌内部实施时，却足足耗费了两年的时间才执行完他原本预估半年的这套计划。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19); background-color: rgb(238, 237, 235);\"><img src=\"data:image/gif;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAADUlEQVQImWNgYGBgAAAABQABh6FO1AAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==\"></span></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/43186a39-9028-4a4f-a599-5d58333a65f9.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=f%2B6Abm11ndVqX0ORnjP6TPKz4dA%3D\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">“我曾负责Palm的设计和用户体验，并且给Palm打上了很多属于我的烙印。当我兴致勃勃加入谷歌实施我的计划时，才意识到在这样的大公司里提出并付诸一个想法有多么复杂，这完全不同于掌控一辆小型灵动自由转换的汽车方向盘，这简直是航空母舰。”</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">虽然不是每个人都能像Duarte重新设计手机操作系统那样雄心勃勃地开展项目，但我们中的许多人都希望在我们工作的公司留下自己的印记。</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">对于规模较小的公司而言，这可能比大公司更容易。</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(192, 200, 209);\">“</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">你在小企业中取得的每一次成功都会被放大一百倍。</span></p><p>&nbsp;—— 招聘高级副总裁Dean Medley</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(192, 200, 209);\">”</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">在一家大公司可能需要数天或数周的提交和批准程序，在小公司里只需要一个敲门。</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">与所有上下级同事带着同样的奋斗目标，完全置身于一个项目中，毫无顾忌的提出你每个一闪而过的想法和意见。</span></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/2d47d45b-f404-44b8-bccb-1aa500e2a703.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=ZYgCmQR5XBc9nTl2McXqA%2FoxnPc%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">带着热情和兴趣工作，在承担更多层次的任务中收获成长，每个人都能看到你的能力，你的潜力，你的业绩。</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">不是螺丝钉，而是顶梁柱。</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong>3</strong></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(174, 163, 162);\">&nbsp;&gt;</strong><strong style=\"color: rgb(125, 116, 108);\">&gt;</strong><strong>勇敢者</strong><strong style=\"color: rgb(125, 116, 108);\">&lt;</strong><strong style=\"color: rgb(174, 163, 162);\">&lt;</strong></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">无论公司大或小，更重要的是有</span><strong>潜力</strong>、有<strong>前景</strong>，而雷塔智能科技就是这样一家公司。</p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19); background-color: rgb(238, 237, 235);\"><img src=\"data:image/gif;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAADUlEQVQImWNgYGBgAAAABQABh6FO1AAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==\"></span><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/71c7710a-2b12-443a-9c02-8b8e665070f6.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=KBV3xlMYWVrluhLwDQKozfxi%2BFQ%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">公司的潜力与气质往往由它的产品体现。</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">认识了超级笔记，也就认识了雷塔。</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">科技 &amp; 文艺</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">当人们前仆后继追随科技热潮亦或是坚守传统领域时，雷塔选择了另外一条路。</span></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/d9b50f08-a70c-4566-aa15-d39cf2bd7b0f.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=cTm3MQHjj9EM41ntRkiRUokbXpw%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">超级笔记是一个基于电子墨水屏，手写体验最接近真实纸笔的</span><strong>电子笔记</strong>，不同于其他电子墨水屏产品主打的阅读，超级笔记强调的是其流畅的书写体验。</p><p><br></p><p>通过基于Linux开发的定制系统、智能手写识别功能以及专门打造的书写加速芯片，超级笔记完美融合了现代科技的智能处理和传统文具的手写体验。</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/adaf6fd2-841c-4c9a-8e15-394246085957.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=OAHxwUkKahCNjjq5sZn1aYxekA0%3D\"></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/2e7ee33f-d5d9-4242-bb04-8c5655cb29ae.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=7w8l6iwb4%2FUDRLqwr25uM5rTW9A%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19); background-color: rgb(238, 237, 235);\"><img src=\"data:image/gif;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAADUlEQVQImWNgYGBgAAAABQABh6FO1AAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==\"></span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">配件上，从封套到笔，每一处都能唤起你满腔的文艺情结，极富文具内涵的封套，搭配随性DIY的电子笔，超级笔记俨然化身一个传统文具。</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">文艺不是超级笔记的目的，而是超级笔记的</span><strong>态度</strong>。雷塔就是这样一家科技与人文相结合的公司，希望通过开辟电子笔记新品类，做文具数字化的先驱。</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/29578ac3-0d9b-48f3-b9ad-295d84ebb090.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=8wFyIeTYuV8a8mXneEfTNWKmjPI%3D\"></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(2, 30, 170);\">▲ 超级笔记企业画报</strong></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">而这份雄心壮志的来源是热爱，绝非什么成功学。</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">自由 &amp; 情怀</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">超级笔记拒绝千篇一律。</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">实用性上，超级笔记追求“轻”、“快”、“灵”。</span></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/b61b70d7-f376-4a35-bd80-58615e309a5a.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=P%2Fl%2Fe2Bo5RhxV2yvM7m5qQ94kQw%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">“轻”，仅重300多g，让设备不再成为负担。</span></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/b125dad3-05b0-4168-adb2-5b9be2c1aeaa.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=n7ShdXQx6hHVsf2QyGTcsD8rOvI%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">“快”，释放电子纸原力，追求极致的手写低延迟，不错过每一个转瞬即逝的灵感。</span></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/2bfb630d-5146-48ce-8a7f-9d6f777a5a1e.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=y5uBaPvRvB8vXKikli65%2FK6iG08%3D\"></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(2, 30, 170);\">▲&nbsp;标签式侧滑栏</strong></p><p><br></p><p>“灵\"，像真实书签一样的侧滑栏，标签之间直接切换，没有实体键的笨拙感，让操作随心所欲。</p><p><br></p><p>在配件上，自由精神也潜藏在超级笔记的每个角落。</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/4f0817e4-a33e-4dc4-bc4a-eff3f6403d8a.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=%2BmEtLcszAYNduEJPk5fKzs%2BUyyQ%3D\"></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(2, 30, 170);\">▲ 封套：超级笔记 vs 其他设备</strong></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/38af5617-29f4-448a-8f88-f0b802488486.gif?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=igrB0TP2kdXmpdE1CG7vcML6yeM%3D\"></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(2, 30, 170);\">▲ 导轨式结构</strong></p><p><br></p><p>超级笔记的封套采用独具一格的<strong>非包边</strong>设计，彰显与众不同的个性，同时独创了<strong>导轨式</strong>结构，自由便捷地安装与拆卸。</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/0bb03d65-cb59-480a-b581-d9e811179443.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=zCWqziXn9R1A74SKfI0ANfCzLuw%3D\"></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(2, 30, 170);\">▲ Supernote的笔，fresh style</strong></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/f00702e1-8e88-4daf-9123-a04583bc8506.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=Z%2Be0Miztz%2FnyF%2B4ykToa5VQYbcg%3D\"></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(2, 30, 170);\">▲ 其他的笔，boring style</strong></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/8fb7f76f-5d54-4c65-ab5d-b39ce19a5e7f.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=qsyfdcveBAB9tAuaKR15VWahiLE%3D\"></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(2, 30, 170);\">▲ 笔尖：超级笔记（左）vs 其他设备</strong></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">超级笔记的笔不再是千篇一律的风格，仅有0.7mm的笔尖精细耐磨，可定制化的笔壳完美还原了传统文具，不止自由，更加有趣。</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">而你的</span><strong>个性、自由、创意</strong>，正是雷塔最爱的基因。</p><p><br></p><p>在做些有意义的事情上，超级笔记也一直在努力。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19); background-color: rgb(238, 237, 235);\"><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/5d75a472-39f4-40db-b54f-8df38fb7a373.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=9ibOA%2BfdWwEjqtazzIaWi%2Bad%2BAE%3D\"><img src=\"data:image/gif;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAADUlEQVQImWNgYGBgAAAABQABh6FO1AAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==\"></span></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(2, 30, 170);\">▲&nbsp;Connected Ink 2018 现场</strong></p><p><br></p><p>在Connected Ink 2018上，超级笔记作为一个融合了电子科技和传统文具的参展品牌，把数字书写的魅力带给了全世界。</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/aeb6bfe0-57fd-4e7d-aa4f-1cd971065314.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=CfzaQcWivykDdu9aqdgDA19ufvc%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p>肩负着文具数字化的使命，超级笔记成为数字文具联盟（DSC）的重要成员，与全球生态圈伙伴分享并讨论数字文具技术解决方案，迈出了推动文具数字化的坚实一步。</p><p><br></p><p>情怀，超级笔记不只是说说而已。</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong>4</strong></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(242, 238, 223);\">&nbsp;</strong><strong style=\"color: rgb(174, 163, 162);\">&gt;</strong><strong style=\"color: rgb(125, 116, 108);\">&gt;</strong><strong>最后</strong><strong style=\"color: rgb(125, 116, 108);\">&lt;</strong><strong style=\"color: rgb(174, 163, 162);\">&lt;</strong></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">也许你不能像李白一样“乘风破浪会有时，直挂云帆济沧海”，成就传奇伟业，但在波澜壮阔的人生大海上航行，时而与善变的海风搏斗，时而与暗藏的礁石抗衡，才是一个人应有的完整历程。</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">有人选择钻进巨轮的舱室度过波澜不惊的一生，唯有勇者会跳上快艇，在自由的气息中劈波斩浪，一同享受风雨过后明媚的阳光和绚丽的彩虹。</span></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/dcbea7aa-2b3e-415b-84d7-88f3c11fe982.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=jZFjttCU25XmYB%2FGk0I5b4donek%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">我们希望找到更多志同道合的小伙伴加入我们，一起打造具有人文温度的科技产品，并将我们的成果分享给世界。</span></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/50c6e166-ddad-47d6-af74-a1df37c010b8.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=gUCWGdRXYqU7yiT3Ahc9rsxdzwc%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\">欢迎加入最富创造力的团队，我们求贤若渴，正在招聘</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\">C++高级软件工程师、C++软件工程师、驱动工程师、自动化测试工程师、硬件测试工程师</strong>等岗位。</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(19, 19, 19);\"><img src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/FH81YqpQrm3EOItdphiatfyFc4ssKSicy4Wl4uQ5m17p5G8NzxoVibEsiaUmx2pcM2ibbbicUjhRU9kqibN3bLTmlTLmg/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\"></span></p>', 'https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/8d141ef4-3939-43ea-bc5c-d6e13268c104.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&Expires=&Signature=xdf2%2F6wJsDsHzBmsKZmipeY1u9w%3D', 'https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/f0d001d3-d6fa-4954-bc98-467091f64944.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&Expires=&Signature=XZkPZrptJ6ad8QWfjHjSQ25c4qo%3D', '0', 'ZH-CN', 52, 51, 10, 4, 15, 14, 'Y', '2019-10-16 22:55:55', 'admin', '2019-11-05 11:27:14', 'admin', '接受波澜不惊的人生？去做个劈波斩浪的勇者吧', '接受波澜不惊的人生？去做个劈波斩浪的勇者吧', '接受波澜不惊的人生？去做个劈波斩浪的勇者吧');
INSERT INTO `t_blog` VALUES (35, 3, '超级笔记supernote', '【笔的前世今生 | 书写工具进化史', '<p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/deeb72e8-f2ea-4c9c-8d26-76bd96cd8a6f.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=zK8oxZwlrMyJcxc4p90RARYirLU%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p>第二次世界大战，美国向日本广岛投放了原子弹，原子弹巨大的威力让人们吃惊不已，也让“原子”这个名字走进了千家万户。</p><p><br></p><p>战争结束后，美国雷诺公司借原子弹的余威开始大做广告宣传“原子笔”，声称原子笔的技术和原子弹一样先进，无需灌墨水，甚至可以在水下书写，定价高达10美元一支。</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/ba97e701-5e7a-4043-9a3c-c8e4be1e437a.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=WK5G%2BUPN98vwl3IFRuh6Fc4qavc%3D\"></p><p><strong>•&nbsp;原子弹爆炸瞬间</strong></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>雷诺独特的宣传和定价策略抓住了人们的好奇心，原子笔开始大卖。后来，香港利丰把原子笔从美国引入香港，把中文名也取为原子笔，代表技术最先进的笔，从此，原子笔开始在中国逐渐风靡。</p><p><br></p><p>除了原子笔，铅笔、羽毛笔又是怎样出现的呢？书写工具经历过怎样的发展历程？</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong>从石块到芦苇杆，书写工具的原始演变</strong></p><p><br></p><p>1994年，肖维等三位科学家在法国阿尔代什省（Ardeche）考察，偶然发现一个被碎石掩埋的大型洞穴，当他们走进洞穴，内部石壁上的景观让他们惊呆了——数百幅壁画呈现在眼前，壁画图像中有冰河期灭绝的各种动物和打猎的早期人类，展示了当时高超的绘画技巧。</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/d5f3e23b-3698-40f7-a8a9-d340a399faba.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=JleL3r6%2BMep5Ulyzd9h9uBS4CHs%3D\"></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(59, 80, 215);\">• 肖维-蓬达尔克洞穴壁画&nbsp;&nbsp;图源@EPA</strong></p><p><br></p><p>经过考古学家鉴定，这些壁画是三万两千到三万六千年前的人类使用打磨过的石块和矿物雕刻在洞穴岩壁上的，这座史前洞穴也被称之为肖维-蓬达尔克洞穴（La Grotte Chauvet-point-d’Arc）。石块、硬骨、矿物等物品就是当时的“笔”，也成为人类最早的书写工具。</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/3b6c4174-9290-4613-a7c1-ede922b22eea.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=Kcmn63BJhIOfKWUBJmUTqNYHmqI%3D\"></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(59, 80, 215);\">• 史前动物</strong></p><p><br></p><p>以石块等硬物做为书写工具持续了很久，直到约公元前4000年，在亚洲的亚美尼亚高原上，幼发拉底河和底格里斯河孕育了一群极富智慧的种族——苏美尔人。</p><p><br></p><p>他们从狩猎转向农耕，建立部落城邦，他们想要记录下来自己的光辉伟业，于是，他们发明了楔形文字，把芦苇杆削尖作为新的书写工具，从此，人类的“笔”开始有了“现代笔”的样子。</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/ee3a7219-f086-42c1-bc89-a5f83ed1431a.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=SsRFD5cIqs86GWxdDeWvEQQet88%3D\"></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(59, 80, 215);\">• 苏美尔人发明的楔形文字</strong></p><p><br></p><p>后来，埃及人改良了芦苇笔，把煤灰和水混作“墨水”，用芦苇笔蘸着“墨水”在莎草纸上写字，沿用数千年之久。</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/a012b78f-acbc-47cb-b4e3-449fc83ead84.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=X0LJ2a%2BH0nQHxPikhs4tWaX8o0o%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(59, 80, 215);\">• 芦苇笔</strong></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong>兽毛笔和羽毛笔，中西方的历史见证</strong></p><p><br></p><p>相传，秦国将军蒙恬打猎时发现受伤的兔子用尾巴拖出的血迹可以组成各种各样的形状，他灵感大发，把兔尾毛剪下插在竹管中，试着用来写字。然而，兔毛带有油脂，不吸墨水，蒙恬非常恼怒，愤然把兔毛笔扔到了石坑里。</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/2b710f4a-701c-45f3-8ce8-5ea65676d4e2.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=ZcW%2FACfhLANmQwlGtx8oFvGjG%2BI%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><strong>• 秦国著名将领蒙恬</strong></p><p><br></p><p>过了几天，蒙恬闲来无趣，把石坑里的兔毛笔拿出来把玩，这次兔毛竟然神奇地吸满了墨水，写字也非常顺滑。原来，石坑里含有碱性石灰水，会去掉兔毛上的油脂。</p><p><br></p><p>由于这支笔是由兔毛和竹子组成，于是蒙恬便在当时笔的写法“聿”字上加了一个“竹”子头，取名为“筆”，如今简写为“笔”。毛笔在中国作为主流书写工具延续了数千年，古代中国的书法和绘画皆是基于毛笔而创作。</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/e87a9d41-0fe7-4ad0-92c3-ba5d1151d93f.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=apq8V7RKHLxs94hQbWqPTrOfbI0%3D\"></p><p><strong>• 文房四宝 笔墨纸砚</strong></p><p><br></p><p>相较于东方的“柔软”，西方更爱硬笔。西元7世纪时，羽毛笔代替芦苇笔成为西方最主流的书写工具。</p><p><br></p><p>羽毛笔的制作材料来自于大型鸟类身上的羽毛，最为普遍的便是鹅毛笔，外观优雅端庄，鹅毛取自于鹅翅膀最外层的五根羽毛，并且是左侧翅膀，因为左侧翅膀羽毛的生长角度更能符合人们右手握笔的习惯。</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/5dff7806-002f-468d-8fe4-c470c24e94eb.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=eRr7vE9gN9UV%2BiR3vKQlFQOovuU%3D\"></p><p><strong>• 优雅的鹅毛笔</strong></p><p><br></p><p>此外，还有用猫头鹰、乌鸦的羽毛做的羽毛笔能写出更细腻的文字，用天鹅毛做的羽毛笔价格昂贵，成为一种奢侈品。</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/2c37efc3-9041-4f4b-a1c0-81738338166c.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=xgHfg0Q2LhaYLTVJxss1oMZYWCk%3D\"></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(59, 80, 215);\">•&nbsp;羽毛笔成为潮流</strong></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong>从石墨到铅笔，站在前人的肩膀上</strong></p><p><br></p><p>1564年，英国牧羊人发现石墨可以在羊身上画记号，当时化学还没有普及，人们把这种石墨称之为“黑铅”，一些有商业头脑的人开始把石墨做成条状物在城市里售卖，这些商人们给这种条状物起了个名字叫做好用的刷子——pencil。人们发现这种刷子不会像羽毛笔一样把墨水弄得到处都是，并且写出来的字还神奇的可以用面包屑和海绵等絮状物擦掉，但是却很容易折断，还会弄脏手。</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/a8dd6c74-9f6f-4fba-b96b-2f443e2a28d8.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=BMlf5aSiGeqKaHKTIqPxJ7wrMf0%3D\"></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(59, 80, 215);\">• 被称为“黑铅”的石墨</strong></p><p><br></p><p>1761年，人们终于解决了铅笔弄脏手的问题。德国化学家法贝儿在石墨中掺入硫磺、树脂，加热凝固后制作出铅笔芯，然后用纸包裹住，新式铅笔出现在了城市的大商场里，然而石墨易断的问题还是没有解决。</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/cba83017-3895-4fa4-bca8-dd6ba62a4998.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=0%2BoQWbNKc1LHvzhyGPs4v%2FYR1AU%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(59, 80, 215);\">• 现存最古老的铅笔模型&nbsp;图源@加速会</strong></p><p><br></p><p>直到1812年，现代铅笔终于问世。让人没想到的是，它竟出自于美国一个普通木匠。这位木匠名叫门罗，他将两片同样凹槽的木条中间嵌入石墨条，用胶水粘住木条，完美解决了石墨易断的问题。到这个时候，铅笔已经全面普及。</p><p><br></p><p>后来，日本人早川德次在1915年发明了一种金属外壳内置弹簧的铅笔，它不仅可以自动弹出笔芯，还节省木材，这就是现代自动铅笔的原型。</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/3a9204eb-4c3b-4e4b-a2c3-da1ac37de84c.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=DEomeTUDli7%2F9KXSrO%2ByUmiRrOs%3D\"></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(59, 80, 215);\">• 自动铅笔</strong></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong>从钢笔到原子笔，引领书写时代革命</strong></p><p><br></p><p>人们对极致书写的追求从未停止，羽毛笔时代，写字必须蘸墨水使用，便利性大打折扣，书写工具需要一次变革。</p><p><br></p><p>英国人布拉马想到了一个办法，他改用银制作笔杆，把墨水裹装笔杆中，连接钢制笔尖，解决了蘸墨的麻烦。但是，笔杆裹墨的方式难以控制墨水，很容易使墨水撒到纸上，毁了整个文本。于是，人们又开始不断地发挥创造力，试图制作出完美的钢笔，仅19世纪一百年间就有400多种钢笔发明出现，然而却都因为漏墨或是出水过慢而被淘汰。</p><p><br></p><p>直到1884年，沃特曼（钢笔品牌Waterman创始人）推出了三裂缝加墨水装置的钢笔。</p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/771ecd4a-4613-4c8f-932f-ee0613ae901c.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=sUPdJ%2Ftt5s5yGHtbl9DOtIJxros%3D\"></p><p>沃特曼本来是一位保险推销员，有一次因为钢笔漏墨，墨水毁掉了一份重要文件，导致合同报废。从此，沃特曼发誓要打造出可以完美控制墨水的钢笔。他开发出三裂缝加墨水装置，利用毛细血管动作原理，令墨水可以稳定流量，完全避免了渗漏。</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/c56600ff-229d-4b1f-963b-c6c886f59983.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=LhvCQl%2B%2BGBTYi2DBdz0AC7Y4F84%3D\"></p><p><strong>• 沃特曼钢笔结构&nbsp;图源Wikipedia</strong></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>这种叫做钢笔的书写工具，一经推出，便席卷整个市场，拥有一支属于自己的钢笔，成为每个文化人的追求，直到现代，依然如此。</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/ee708acc-18e6-42a0-8f60-a849c3189af9.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=FZADMT1ggy8FWyXYR1JwANCNyM4%3D\"></p><p><strong>• Waterman如今依然是钢笔领军品牌之一</strong></p><p><br></p><p>钢笔是幸运的，就在沃特曼推出钢笔仅仅4年后，美国的劳比便提出了一种理想化的新概念笔，它和钢笔以及之前的笔都不同，劳比认为可以在笔尖上加一个圆珠，书写时由圆珠的滚动来延伸墨水。</p><p><br></p><p>现在看来，这种创造性的想法几乎就是现代圆珠笔的原型。然而，现实对劳比来说是苦涩的，当时的圆珠设计完全没法控制墨水的流量，它失败了，那个时代属于沃特曼钢笔。</p><p><br></p><p>半个世纪后，匈牙利记者拉兹罗从报纸印刷速干技术中取得灵感，他试着制作了速干墨水笔管，然后把一颗小钢珠装在笔尖，写字时，滚动的小钢珠可以非常顺滑的留下笔迹，不写时小钢珠又可以堵住墨水，拉兹罗真正地把劳比的想法付诸实践，世界上第一支原子笔就此诞生。</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/84eb2e32-38a3-46ae-ab56-6e0b73152088.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=zmshh3%2F7vVu8rIRr33q5dWV65%2Fc%3D\"></p><p><strong>• 小小的圆珠笔头蕴含着强大的工艺</strong></p><p><br></p><p>英国政府开始应用这种有史以来最便捷的书写工具，美国商人们也开始在市场上高价销售原子笔，各国都开始效仿制作，原子笔的成本也越来越低，廉价而又实用成为原子笔的标签，也帮助原子笔从西方到东方席卷全球，成为了全世界使用最普遍的书写工具。</p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/3f86ce53-3446-4ddb-8e05-ce221327c601.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=ruxARj4Z9GRwjFnx1CWG%2FWzg5OQ%3D\"></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(59, 80, 215);\">• 原子笔风靡全球</strong></p><p><br></p><p>后来，日本企业在原子笔的基础上又开发了中性笔和宝珠笔，中性笔的墨水不粘稠，书写品质相对更好，与传统原子笔不同的手感和外观样式给人们提供了更多的选择。</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/6185f25d-883a-4ec1-bbc0-aa3f36b9f0b1.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=%2F%2BvJPtKNemMXmGLprSz4OsLFqrU%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><strong>电子化时代，书写何去何从</strong></p><p><br></p><p>书写工具的变迁，也是人类文明不断进化的写照。电子化时代，书写的功能必然发生变化。</p><p><br></p><p>有人说，未来将不会再有书写的位置。电子文档将取代书本，键盘将取代纸笔，语音交互将取代手写触摸（老罗抱着TNT笑而不语）...</p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/151a3223-a20a-47be-bb27-2fd08c0c5890.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=qrwLlfbGcRXBpjV2ZdPFbPG4ufo%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><strong>• 电子化办公成为趋势</strong></p><p><br></p><p>书写真的会在数字时代消失吗？</p><p><br></p><p>培根曾写道：“阅读使人充实，而书写使人精细。”书写的乐趣与意义是计算机无法比拟的，笔尖在纸上的跃动所带来的体验是液晶屏无法带来的。</p><p><br></p><p>书写不会被取代，它只是以多种形式而存在。</p><p><br></p><p>这个时代，记录信息可能并不需要传统的书写。但很多的创新，正在将书写带回到现代世界，努力找到电子设备与传统书写的平衡点。</p><p><br></p><p>1984年，Wacom推出全球首款使用「无线电子笔」的手写板“WT系列”。</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/a92c5c66-94dc-4874-8412-f95ccd045dd2.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=0qBgpj%2Bkt0VaGw0ALqy2sAWzbRk%3D\"></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(2, 30, 170);\">• Wacom-460M</strong></p><p><br></p><p>35年间，Wacom专注于笔输入领域的研发。截至2013年，Wacom在数字书写领域市场占有率超过80%，成为数字书写的代名词。</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/2bd32085-ad2d-4776-9b57-48ecf55ba3b6.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=jKpb0f1NxOTAgvoVIc2bk%2FyISCw%3D\"></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(2, 30, 170);\">• 图源 @Wacom中国</strong></p><p><br></p><p>1997年，数字纸张的领域也迎来突破。美国麻省理工学院的媒体实验室里诞生了未来电子纸制造的核心技术——E-ink电子墨水。</p><p><br></p><p>这种技术，让数字屏幕能像纸一样靠反射自然光来显示内容，电子墨水屏还像纸一样具有很大的柔性，这一切都让数字屏幕可以更好的模拟纸张的质感。</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/69a65cdb-6d92-4e05-a45f-e9d8ef5baa8c.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=XQ%2B55CXyTVeT%2FCGpPPdpUvwMCqg%3D\"></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(2, 30, 170);\">• 电子墨水</strong></p><p><br></p><p>“让书写回归本质”，成熟的电磁笔技术与电子墨水屏相融合，创造出一种电子化时代自然书写与智能处理相结合的书写工具新方案——超级笔记。“最传统”纸的质感，笔的触感，“文具化”的外观，Supernote把笔的温度重新带给数字世界。</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/1d9343be-3e3e-417a-85ad-3b64fc094cb5.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=hzBisAoMKhWYmNhczZHLKXqGRhk%3D\"></p><p><strong>• 超级笔记，为写而生</strong></p><p><br></p><p>诚然，相比于书写，键盘是更高效的录入方式。但是，对录入效率不敏感的原创思考过程，<strong>一笔一划，字里行间却更能与思维的过程合拍</strong>，如切如磋，如琢如磨。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><blockquote>正如埃及书记员4000年前所说：人终将化为腐朽，肉体归入泥土；其亲皆会化为尘埃。唯书写使其永存于记忆。</blockquote><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">*参考资料</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">San Francisco Bay Area, United States.法国 阿尔代什省彩绘洞穴</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Steven Roger Fischer. A History of Writing, Reaktion Books,London, 2001</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Wikipedia:Lewis Edson Waterman</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">加速会：KOL观察团.&nbsp;科普 | 一支铅笔的诞生</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><h2><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">视觉中国图画历史:钢笔的诞生竟是源于一根羽毛</span></h2><p><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">腾讯网：66年卖出1000亿支，中国造不出来的圆珠笔</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Wacom中国：行稳致远 Wacom迎35周年</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">ZAKER:圆珠笔的浪费使用你知道吗？关于笔你知道多少？</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/FH81YqpQrm3EOItdphiatfyFc4ssKSicy4Wl4uQ5m17p5G8NzxoVibEsiaUmx2pcM2ibbbicUjhRU9kqibN3bLTmlTLmg/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\"></p>', 'https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/697ba034-14a1-469d-a66f-1ede2a30dc6d.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&Expires=&Signature=c%2BaYabkfasFaf9eeoarmdXcknio%3D', 'https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/04db11d7-4049-4cdd-ac80-b778b2119764.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&Expires=&Signature=5NuA3JXRLZsZ4Bqt1VNUCF4qkkQ%3D', '0', 'ZH-CN', 53, 52, 10, 3, 10, 9, 'Y', '2019-10-16 23:11:11', 'admin', '2019-11-05 16:08:15', 'admin', '【笔的前世今生 | 书写工具进化史22', '【笔的前世今生 | 书写工具进化史', '【笔的前世今生 | 书写工具进化史');
INSERT INTO `t_blog` VALUES (57, 4, 'Supernote', 'The history of electronic paper', '<p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/632c8014-6ec1-404f-807b-1364cc833825.jpg?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=bYZbTs4zWPfP0TGpg94GEYId5Dc%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">In 2007, Amazon released the first generation of e-reader Kindle, which is</span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">equipped with a 6-inch 4th-order electronic paper ink screen.With the</span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">popularity of the Kindle, e-paper is truly familiar to consumers.</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">Electronic Paper (ePaper) is a display technology that mimics the visual</span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">perception of printing and writing on paper.</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/2b0f8cdc-e954-4b17-8f63-0d0c4fa1cfb8.jpg?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=V53dfMiPAALrNjjGLa3OmKDOXF0%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">Unlike ordinary flat panel displays that display images with illuminating </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">light, electronic papers use electrophoresis display (EPD) as a display </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">panel. They rely on reflected ambient light to display images, which are </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">more comfortable to read and can display images.It is still clearly visible </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">under direct sunlight, and has a wide viewing angle, theoretically up to </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">180 degrees.</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">E-paper is flexible and low-power, and is widely used in reading and </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">writing, mobile wear, electronic shelf labels, electronic signage, </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">architecture and design.</span></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/dd52b8f8-6080-4db4-a359-d933ef60d785.jpg?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=0o5ysvGxgrhOpIuYDo799dhI4h8%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">However, looking back on the past, the development of electronic paper </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">has also encountered many crises.From the birth of the 1960s to the real </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">large-scale application at the beginning of this century, e-paper has </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">experienced many difficulties and obstacles.</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">In the era of LCD technology, how did e-paper break through?</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><h2>Electronic paper or LCD screen? Panasonic’s hesitation</h2><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">The first electronic paper in history was not from E Ink, but a famous </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">Japanese electrical appliance company, Panasonic.</span></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/8cdf29ca-10de-44da-8afd-9ff8fc3c7942.jpg?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=fG67uVsAzYJeeo6zFxybg%2FOmpeg%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">In 1968, the Radio Corporation of America (RCA) published the theory that </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">“displays can be made using liquid crystal materials.” This theory later </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">became the basis for the development of liquid crystal panels.</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">At the time, 太田勋夫, who developed the electronic photo display liquid, </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">was shocked when he heard the news. He immediately started researching </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">it. After the research, he boldly came to the conclusion that electrophoresis </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">technology is more promising than liquid crystal technology in display </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">applications.</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">太田勋夫 began to develop electrophoretic electronic paper. In 1969, he </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">applied for several patents related to electrophoresis technology.</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">In the 1970s, Panasonic began to market its products.At the same time, </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">another electronic paper technology “Gyricon” was born in 1970. It was </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">developed by the famous Xerox Palo Alto Research Center, where the </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">mouse, laser printer, graphical user interface and page description </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">language Interpress were born.Major inventions that affect the historical </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">process of the 20th century.</span></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/453fd73d-c357-4d10-88e3-d435ede4708b.jpg?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=iB9PjkJc1vaOvprdz5anA2H6dUs%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">However, the good times did not last long. In 1976, Panasonic suddenly </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">chose to stop developing electronic paper and turned to the LCD screen </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">field.</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">It may be because the product repair rate at that time was extremely high, </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">and it may be due to the envy of the Sharp LCD display calculator.</span></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/85c5199d-8dc6-4613-81a3-760ba32991cb.jpg?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=7YCk1eBIGVYXShmVmryiRo68w0Y%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">From the perspective of interests, Panasonic’s choice may be right. After </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">several decades, LCD monitors have brought huge gains to Panasonic.</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">However, the development of electronic paper has thus stagnate, and </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">Xerox’s Gyricon has only lived in the laboratory.</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">Will e-paper be going to fail?</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><h2>The development of electronic paper technology, the birth of E Ink</h2><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">It was not until the 1990s that after 20 years of decadence, electronic paper </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">finally ushered in spring.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">In 1995, in the MIT Media Lab, Professor Neil Gershenfeld, physicist </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">Joseph Jacobson, mathematics student Barrett Comiskey, and mechanical </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">engineering student JD Albert co-created E Ink.</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">Electrophoretic ink technology is commonly known as electronic ink.The </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">electronic ink is coated on a layer of plastic film, and then attached to a </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">thin film transistor (TFT) circuit, and controlled by a driver IC to form a </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">pixel pattern to create an electronic paper display (EPD).</span></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/6bb11760-cac7-481d-8af3-710010ef5384.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=9w546qDUi02F6x4fu6%2FKMzz8cCI%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">They then applied for a patent and in 1997 they teamed up to create the E </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">Ink company.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">Since then, electronic paper has begun to enter the public’s field of vision.</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><h2>The road to commercialization of electronic paper, E Ink dominates</h2><h2>the field of electronic paper</h2><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">Through the wave of e-ink technology, in May 1999, E Ink launched an </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">outdoor e-paper called Immedia for advertising.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">However, what really caused a sensation was the “e-newspaper” </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">conceptual model launched by IBM in the same year.</span></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/fac79bab-a66f-49ee-9cbf-b12b764274ca.jpg?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=HHprhnQygEP9darMi9CCDwDbqfY%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">In 1999, at the largest newspaper exhibition in the United States, IBM </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">demonstrated an “e-newspaper” that could read text and image </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">information through an electronic display layer, attracting attention from </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">the newspaper publishing industry around the world.The New York Times </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">and The Washington Post spoke highly of the “e-newspaper”, claiming that </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">this e-reading has revolutionary significance, and BusinessWeek also </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">awarded the annual IDEA American Industrial Design Award to the </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">“Electronic Newspaper.”In recognition of its cross-age value in terms of </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">printing cost savings and news timeliness.</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/932e7b4c-016d-4ca5-80e3-c46c9d36e773.jpg?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=LE7an50rlyzeJa1Hegez6cjwFRg%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">Robert Steinbugler, who is the chief designer of IBM and the head of the </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">“electronic newspaper” project, proudly said: “People will be able to see the </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">part of the newspaper that they are most interested in anytime and anywhere, and </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">the electronic newspaper will be spread all over the world.”</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">However, at that time, the development of the network had not reached </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">the level that could support this idea. The “electronic newspaper” </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">eventually became the fantasy of IBM.However, it seems now that the </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">concept of customized information flow contained in the “electronic </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">newspaper” happens to be the focus of competition among major Internet </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">giants in more than a decade.</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">IBM’s “failure” did not delay the development of e-paper. From 00 to 2002, </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">new technologies such as curled e-paper and color e-paper were </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">introduced.</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">In 2004, the road to commercialization of electronic paper finally ushered </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">in a historic breakthrough, and Sony once again became a pioneer in the </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">industry.</span></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/ea262913-d985-4288-b7d8-fe8e37bdc848.jpg?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=PCyQrdmPN%2B8d8KXn64gd1Zx9J4M%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">The world’s first commercially available electronic paper “LIBRIe”, </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">powered by Eink and Philips, was produced by Sony.The LIBRIe measures </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">190×126×13mm and weighs only 190g. It only needs 4 batteries and 7 </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">batteries to browse 10,000 pages. The careful Sony also provides users </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">with 4 kinds of contrast adjustment and recording functions also joined by </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">Sony to LIBRIe.</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">The launch of the electronic paper of 40,000 yen has attracted worldwide </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">attention and, more importantly, it has led to new developments in the </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">electronic paper industry.</span></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/018421f1-a845-451d-a375-379149415cf7.jpg?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=3j2EIJHnlk2V%2FiPpyyF1lM4GhRg%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">Electronic companies around the world are rushing to develop e-paper </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">products, and they are aware of the huge potential of the e-paper market.</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">In 2005, Seiko released the first electronic ink watch called Spectrum </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">SVRD001, which looks like a crafted bracelet that uses the softness of </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">electronic paper to make it extremely thin and low-power design effect.</span></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/e50d1287-5b77-4812-8566-a3687205cf49.jpg?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=QnJ3V6Zsxz6mF55gA%2FEbevp%2FbKc%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">In 2007, Amazon released the first generation of e-reader Kindle. What </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">Amazon didn’t expect was that this e-ink screen product was sold out for </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">five hours after it was sold. Amazon will not be able to resume supply until </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">several months later。</span></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/36215c56-cef5-420d-959e-3676ea24af30.jpg?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=kByQfPxmgRFI2WjgfWHi9p0iEAk%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">On June 1, 2009, E Ink announced that it will be acquired by its major </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">business partner Yuan Tai for more than US$400 million, which has </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">accelerated the development of electronic paper technology.And, by 2012, </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">E Ink acquired SiPix, one of only a few competitors.</span></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/b3cbb687-1348-4b85-8a03-2c358ac4f1ea.jpg?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=FNUS8qFdSk1vNvdkCv2aV9oguek%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">By this time, most of the electronic paper products used E Ink’s </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">technology.With about 90% of the electronic paper market share, E Ink </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">finally established the “electronic paper” empire.</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><h2>The impact of the IPAD? Electronic paper goes its own way</h2><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">E Ink looks to the farther future, but this road will not be smooth.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">In the early morning of January 28th, 2010, Steve Jobs, who was slightly </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">gaunt, stood on the podium of the Yerba Buena Art Center in San </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">Francisco: “Apple will bring you a revolutionary new product… its size is </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">between IPHONE and MACBOOK.In the meantime, it can watch videos, </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">listen to music, play games, read e-books… the experience it brings will be </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">unprecedented.”</span></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">The first generation of IPAD was presented to the world and opened the </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">curtain of modern tablet computers.The color display and video fluency </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">brought by the LCD panel are unmatched by electronic paper, and there </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">will be more and more tablet terminal devices equipped with LCD screens </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">in the future.Later, the IPAD even added a stylus.</span></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/48e00b0b-da4c-4951-9a16-11d65da2d057.jpg?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=TrVJfohZDAGv3jfpSVqipBwea78%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">The industry is worried, can the electronic paper market develop </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">smoothly?</span></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">At the crossroads, E Ink resolutely chose to stick to his own path and take </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">advantage of the unique features of e-paper.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">Maybe you didn’t notice that e-paper has been used in every corner.</span></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/6d43c485-8ed7-4c04-84d3-0b610aee37f2.jpg?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=MhpM3V0KsHIxiuU3j6aZfA8LVxg%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">Some bus stop signs have been equipped with electronic paper screens, </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">which display bus line information in real time and can be charged by solar </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">energy.</span></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/f6bad7cb-65de-4645-a7f9-5896201a87bb.jpg?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=t7FMqXd3tYB4R9mYzZ030%2B9xcjY%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">This is the e-paper label in the retail store, which can change the price </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">information at any time, especially for fresh foods with large seasonal </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">changes, which can reduce the waste of a large amount of </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">ingredients.E-paper labels can reduce paper printing, low cost, low power </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">consumption, battery life can be used for more than 5 years, and because of </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">the non-viewing characteristics of e-paper, the shelves from the top to the </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">bottom can be seen at all.It is still clearly visible under strong light.</span></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/53c3b702-b8d0-42c6-b9f5-29a3cf2051c3.png?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=ncAR05EkxmbLas0AkKsUwvAvQKg%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">This is an electronic paper whiteboard from QuirkLogic, a high-contrast 42-</span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">inch screen with an ultra-wide viewing angle that displays content as comfortable as </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">real paper, touch-handwriting is very smooth, and has </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">networking capabilities.</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/c6621d04-f6d7-4afe-bf8e-02fbd56bcdfb.jpg?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=2t3UCiNxprNFBIZAs3aXyPYVuQU%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">The ParceLive e-paper logistics label can display information such as the </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">arrival location and the current status of the goods on the screen, allowing </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">users to track the logistics dynamics at any time, and can update the </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">shipping destination at any time, so that the transport personnel can easily </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">make corresponding changes.</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/a929f415-0313-4d0d-9352-5956c85d7a90.jpg?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=10A%2FzjLo%2F76qOobbaoqPoyDYv%2Fs%3D\">\\</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">12 pieces of 32-inch color electronic paper constitute the National Palace </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">Museum in Taipei, “The Formation of National Treasures — Special </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">Exhibition of Paintings and Calligraphy”, 72 classic national treasures of </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">calligraphy and painting works in turn, electronic paper’s self-illuminating </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">eye protection features allow visitors to observe the national treasure </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">comfortablyEvery detail, low power consumption and low heat </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">characteristics make the environmental temperature of the collection </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">unaffected. Electronic paper has become the first choice for art exhibitions </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">in recent years.</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/e7ee31b7-653f-437f-92fc-24f911299cb3.jpg?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=HG6av%2F4vAtrtzpZBmJACnrwpjO0%3D\"></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">Electronic paper is also used in the field of stationery. Supernote provides a </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">new digital note solution with a handwriting experience close to the real </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">pen and paper. It combines natural writing, intelligent processing and </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">multi-end interconnection. The Supernotes are on the way of stationery </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">digitization.</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">What will happen to the future of electronic paper?We will wait and see.</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><h3><br></h3><p><em class=\"ql-size-large\">Reference materials</em></p><p><br></p><ul><li><em class=\"ql-size-large\">Heikenfeld(2011).A critical review of the present and future prospects </em></li></ul><p><em class=\"ql-size-large\"> for electronicpaper.J.Soc.Inf.Display.19</em></p><p><em class=\"ql-size-large\"> (2):129.doi:10.1889/JSID19.2.129.IRex Takes On The </em></p><p><em class=\"ql-size-large\"> Kindle.Forbes.2008–09–23.Retrieved 2008–11–06.Genuth,Iddo.The </em></p><p><em class=\"ql-size-large\"> Future of Electronic Paper.The Future Of Things.Retrieved 2 March </em></p><p><em class=\"ql-size-large\"> 2015.</em></p><p><br></p><ul><li><span class=\"ql-size-large\">Comiskey,B.;Albert,J.D.;Yoshizawa,H.;Jacobson,J.(1998).”An </span></li></ul><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\"> electrophoretic ink for all-printed reflective electronic </span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\"> displays”.Nature.394(6690):253–255.doi:10.1038/28349.</span></p><p><br></p><ul><li><span class=\"ql-size-large\">Chen Yuwen, Qian Jinwei. The Status Quo and Future Development of </span></li></ul><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\"> Electronic Paper[J]. Modern display, 2009(3):54–57.</span></p><p><br></p><ul><li><span class=\"ql-size-large\">ZOL: From carrot to 4 milliseconds, 120 years of LCD development</span></li></ul><p><br></p><ul><li><span class=\"ql-size-large\">Japanese Society BP: What is electronic paper?</span></li></ul><p><br></p><ul><li><span class=\"ql-size-large\">Yesky: SONY LIBRIe’s world’s first e-book</span></li></ul><p><br></p><ul><li><span class=\"ql-size-large\">Tencent Digital: The history of smart watches has been born in 1971</span></li></ul><p><br></p><ul><li><span class=\"ql-size-large\">E Ink: :cn:.eink.com</span></li></ul>', 'https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/1b6fcb61-01ff-4691-86b1-be6531203f36.jpg?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&Expires=&Signature=tl%2BvgUoCErZS9NHuxpbc82ao%2BE8%3D', 'https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/d88fea0e-e1ed-419d-9959-678f5b37939a.jpg?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&Expires=&Signature=9JcAzHl4De75H56PWkWKRYs%2Fjkg%3D', '0', 'EN', 18, 18, 0, 1, 2, 2, 'N', '2019-11-01 13:56:53', 'admin', '2019-11-05 11:27:49', 'admin', 'The history of electronic paper', 'The history of electronic paper', 'The history of electronic paper');
INSERT INTO `t_blog` VALUES (58, 5, 'ff地方大师傅d\'s', '你的手机地方 ', '<h1>ds舒服</h1><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\">啊大大阿达啊啊发防擦的打打打阿达阿三打算大撒大苏打啊 打</span></p><p><span class=\"ql-size-large\"><span class=\"ql-cursor\">﻿</span></span><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/025bc9c8-5d35-41c4-9b2a-80e3034ebcf3.jpg?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=2OR5DrhDx44DxNHvmQYbNOTATu8%3D\"><img src=\"https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/1733118f-a7f7-4c66-9b1b-5eb80102d608.jpg?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&amp;Expires=&amp;Signature=PMIThzxRS9r8XUdmj%2FzckVmYI2Q%3D\"></p>', 'https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/d1889725-7c05-443c-905b-03b3fb6cf1be.jpg?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&Expires=&Signature=xNabQ%2FTekrNqC6ZWsicKQWVgfvs%3D', 'https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/05ca677f-cf14-4a6b-b526-c739b175ee07.jpg?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&Expires=&Signature=4vwxETpx1ng2qQoiCSu%2B%2FhQQt2A%3D', '0', 'ZH-CN', 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'N', '2019-11-01 15:05:06', 'admin', '2019-11-01 15:05:11', 'admin', '11', 'fff', 'hhh');
INSERT INTO `t_blog` VALUES (59, 6, '55', '55', '<pre class=\"ql-syntax\" spellcheck=\"false\">In 2007, Amazon released the first generation of e-reader Kindle, which is equipped with a 6-inch 4th-order electronic paper ink screen.With the popularity of the Kindle, e-paper is truly familiar to consumers.\nElectronic Paper (ePaper) is a display technology that mimics the visual perception of printing and writing on paper.\n\nE-paper enthusiasts gathering organized by netizen “Tuanzi”\nUnlike ordinary flat panel displays that display images with illuminating light, electronic papers use electrophoresis display (EPD) as a display panel. They rely on reflected ambient light to display images, which are more comfortable to read and can display images.It is still clearly visible under direct sunlight, and has a wide viewing angle, theoretically up to 180 degrees.\nE-paper is flexible and low-power, and is widely used in reading and writing, mobile wear, electronic shelf labels, electronic signage, architecture and design.\n\nHowever, looking back on the past, the development of electronic paper has also encountered many crises.From the birth of the 1960s to the real large-scale application at the beginning of this century, e-paper has experienced many difficulties and obstacles.\nIn the era of LCD technology, how did e-paper break through?\nElectronic paper or LCD screen? Panasonic’s hesitation\nThe first electronic paper in history was not from E Ink, but a famous Japanese electrical appliance company, Panasonic.\n\nPanasonic\nIn 1968, the Radio Corporation of America (RCA) published the theory that “displays can be made using liquid crystal materials.” This theory later became the basis for the development of liquid crystal panels.\nAt the time, 太田勋夫, who developed the electronic photo display liquid, was shocked when he heard the news. He immediately started researching it. After the research, he boldly came to the conclusion that electrophoresis technology is more promising than liquid crystal technology in display applications.\n太田勋夫 began to develop electrophoretic electronic paper. In 1969, he applied for several patents related to electrophoresis technology.\nIn the 1970s, Panasonic began to market its products.At the same time, another electronic paper technology “Gyricon” was born in 1970. It was developed by the famous Xerox Palo Alto Research Center, where the mouse, laser printer, graphical user interface and page description language Interpress were born.Major inventions that affect the historical process of the 20th century.\n\nPalo Alto Research Center\nHowever, the good times did not last long. In 1976, Panasonic suddenly chose to stop developing electronic paper and turned to the LCD screen field.\nIt may be because the product repair rate at that time was extremely high, and it may be due to the envy of the Sharp LCD display calculator.\n\nThe earliest LCD calculator Sharp EL-8020\nFrom the perspective of interests, Panasonic’s choice may be right. After several decades, LCD monitors have brought huge gains to Panasonic.\nHowever, the development of electronic paper has thus stagnate, and Xerox’s Gyricon has only lived in the laboratory.\nWill e-paper be going to fail?\nThe development of electronic paper technology, the birth of E Ink\nIt was not until the 1990s that after 20 years of decadence, electronic paper finally ushered in spring.\nIn 1995, in the MIT Media Lab, Professor Neil Gershenfeld, physicist Joseph Jacobson, mathematics student Barrett Comiskey, and mechanical engineering student JD Albert co-created E Ink.\nElectrophoretic ink technology is commonly known as electronic ink.The electronic ink is coated on a layer of plastic film, and then attached to a thin film transistor (TFT) circuit, and controlled by a driver IC to form a pixel pattern to create an electronic paper display (EPD).\n\nElectrophoretic electronic ink technology\nThey then applied for a patent and in 1997 they teamed up to create the E Ink company.\nSince then, electronic paper has begun to enter the public’s field of vision.\nThe road to commercialization of electronic paper, E Ink dominates the field of electronic paper\nThrough the wave of e-ink technology, in May 1999, E Ink launched an outdoor e-paper called Immedia for advertising.\nHowever, what really caused a sensation was the “e-newspaper” conceptual model launched by IBM in the same year.\n\nIBM e-newspaper conceptual model\nIn 1999, at the largest newspaper exhibition in the United States, IBM demonstrated an “e-newspaper” that could read text and image information through an electronic display layer, attracting attention from the newspaper publishing industry around the world.The New York Times and The Washington Post spoke highly of the “e-newspaper”, claiming that this e-reading has revolutionary significance, and BusinessWeek also awarded the annual IDEA American Industrial Design Award to the “Electronic Newspaper.”In recognition of its cross-age value in terms of printing cost savings and news timeliness.\n\nIDEA American Industrial Design Excellence Award\nRobert Steinbugler, who is the chief designer of IBM and the head of the “electronic newspaper” project, proudly said: “People will be able to see the part of the newspaper that they are most interested in anytime and anywhere, and the electronic newspaper will be spread all over the world.”\nHowever, at that time, the development of the network had not reached the level that could support this idea. The “electronic newspaper” eventually became the fantasy of IBM.However, it seems now that the concept of customized information flow contained in the “electronic newspaper” happens to be the focus of competition among major Internet giants in more than a decade.\nIBM’s “failure” did not delay the development of e-paper. From 00 to 2002, new technologies such as curled e-paper and color e-paper were introduced.\nIn 2004, the road to commercialization of electronic paper finally ushered in a historic breakthrough, and Sony once again became a pioneer in the industry.\n\nSony LIBRle\nThe world’s first commercially available electronic paper “LIBRIe”, powered by Eink and Philips, was produced by Sony.The LIBRIe measures 190×126×13mm and weighs only 190g. It only needs 4 batteries and 7 batteries to browse 10,000 pages. The careful Sony also provides users with 4 kinds of contrast adjustment and recording functions also joined by Sony to LIBRIe.\nThe launch of the electronic paper of 40,000 yen has attracted worldwide attention and, more importantly, it has led to new developments in the electronic paper industry.\n\nElectronic companies around the world are rushing to develop e-paper products, and they are aware of the huge potential of the e-paper market.\nIn 2005, Seiko released the first electronic ink watch called Spectrum SVRD001, which looks like a crafted bracelet that uses the softness of electronic paper to make it extremely thin and low-power design effect.\n\nSpectrum SVRD001 Watch\nIn 2007, Amazon released the first generation of e-reader Kindle. What Amazon didn’t expect was that this e-ink screen product was sold out for five hours after it was sold. Amazon will not be able to resume supply until several months later。\n\nKindle becomes the iconic product of electronic ink screen\nOn June 1, 2009, E Ink announced that it will be acquired by its major business partner Yuan Tai for more than US$400 million, which has accelerated the development of electronic paper technology.And, by 2012, E Ink acquired SiPix, one of only a few competitors.\n\nBy this time, most of the electronic paper products used E Ink’s technology.With about 90% of the electronic paper market share, E Ink finally established the “electronic paper” empire.\nThe impact of the IPAD? Electronic paper goes its own way\nE Ink looks to the farther future, but this road will not be smooth.\nIn the early morning of January 28th, 2010, Steve Jobs, who was slightly gaunt, stood on the podium of the Yerba Buena Art Center in San Francisco: “Apple will bring you a revolutionary new product… its size is between IPHONE and MACBOOK.In the meantime, it can watch videos, listen to music, play games, read e-books… the experience it brings will be unprecedented.”\nThe first generation of IPAD was presented to the world and opened the curtain of modern tablet computers.The color display and video fluency brought by the LCD panel are unmatched by electronic paper, and there will be more and more tablet terminal devices equipped with LCD screens in the future.Later, the IPAD even added a stylus.\n\nThe comfortable layout on the stage shows the simplicity and ease of use of the iPad\nThe industry is worried, can the electronic paper market develop smoothly?\nAt the crossroads, E Ink resolutely chose to stick to his own path and take advantage of the unique features of e-paper.\nMaybe you didn’t notice that e-paper has been used in every corner.\n\nSome bus stop signs have been equipped with electronic paper screens, which display bus line information in real time and can be charged by solar energy.\n\nThis is the e-paper label in the retail store, which can change the price information at any time, especially for fresh foods with large seasonal changes, which can reduce the waste of a large amount of ingredients.E-paper labels can reduce paper printing, low cost, low power consumption, battery life can be used for more than 5 years, and because of the non-viewing characteristics of e-paper, the shelves from the top to the bottom can be seen at all.It is still clearly visible under strong light.\n\nThis is an electronic paper whiteboard from QuirkLogic, a high-contrast 42-inch screen with an ultra-wide viewing angle that displays content as comfortable as real paper, touch-handwriting is very smooth, and has networking capabilities.\n\nThe ParceLive e-paper logistics label can display information such as the arrival location and the current status of the goods on the screen, allowing users to track the logistics dynamics at any time, and can update the shipping destination at any time, so that the transport personnel can easily make corresponding changes.\n\n12 pieces of 32-inch color electronic paper constitute the National Palace Museum in Taipei, “The Formation of National Treasures — Special Exhibition of Paintings and Calligraphy”, 72 classic national treasures of calligraphy and painting works in turn, electronic paper’s self-illuminating eye protection features allow visitors to observe the national treasure comfortablyEvery detail, low power consumption and low heat characteristics make the environmental temperature of the collection unaffected. Electronic paper has become the first choice for art exhibitions in recent years.\n\nElectronic paper is also used in the field of stationery. Supernote provides a new digital note solution with a handwriting experience close to the real pen and paper. It combines natural writing, intelligent processing and multi-end interconnection. The Supernotes are on the way of stationery digitization.\nWhat will happen to the future of electronic paper?We will wait and see.\nReference materials\nHeikenfeld(2011).A critical review of the present and future prospects for electronicpaper.J.Soc.Inf.Display.19(2):129.doi:10.1889/JSID19.2.129.IRex Takes On The Kindle.Forbes.2008–09–23.Retrieved 2008–11–06.Genuth,Iddo.The Future of Electronic Paper.The Future Of Things.Retrieved 2 March 2015.\nComiskey,B.;Albert,J.D.;Yoshizawa,H.;Jacobson,J.(1998).”An electrophoretic ink for all-printed reflective electronic displays”.Nature.394(6690):253–255.doi:10.1038/28349.\nChen Yuwen, Qian Jinwei. The Status Quo and Future Development of Electronic Paper[J]. Modern display, 2009(3):54–57.\nZOL: From carrot to 4 milliseconds, 120 years of LCD development\nJapanese Society BP: What is electronic paper?\nYesky: SONY LIBRIe’s world’s first e-book\nTencent Digital: The history of smart watches has been born in 1971\nE Ink: :cn:.eink.com\n</pre><p><br></p>', 'https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/8df78905-8005-4231-a225-181f968e2d1d.jpg?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&Expires=&Signature=FVZXT1e27oQDZGGONDX3cAln1Ac%3D', 'https://test-cms.cn-sh2.ufileos.com/ab4514b0-7adc-44c5-9fd4-5d0ff71c5179.jpg?UCloudPublicKey=rDlR5TKlbJ9czJLkJrNttUfkJaudoVi%2Br%2BSksVk3XFKjvmr2ue%2Fyc%2FuO2TdhyBpo&Expires=&Signature=wvFDOwQCtPGY%2BelE9OU9CLJOXYk%3D', '2', 'ZH-CN', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'N', '2019-11-01 15:36:57', 'admin', '2019-11-01 15:36:57', 'admin', '111', 'fff', 'nnnn');
